## ğŸ—„ï¸ Loading example

```python
from datasets import load_dataset

# forum style, temporal reasoning
ds = load_dataset("zeinabTaghavi/ImpliRet",
                  name="multispeaker",
                  split="temporal")

print(ds[0]["question"])
print(ds[0]["pos_document"])
```

